description:
Life is stressful! Find out how stressed you really are by taking this Stress Test & measure your stress level. Download this useful mental health app and test yourself!

Our Stress Test will discover your stress level RIGHT NOW! You are not earning enough money? Are you in a constant hurry to meet the deadlines? You don’t have time for yourself? Do you feel like you just want to run away from everything? We are constantly facing with different types of stress that can have a serious negative effect on our mental health. Download this useful mental health app and discover if you have symptoms of depression.There are many stress symptoms including headaches, low energy, insomnia, constant worrying, and nervous behavior. We are not always aware that we are experiencing stress symptoms. So, take our stress test online and learn how to manage stress. Mental health affects how we feel, think, and act, so it is necessary to improve our mental health. This useful psychology app will provide useful indication about your stress level. Stress testing can help you measure your stress level and learn how to handle stress. Reduce stress and do not let it get the best of you! Take a Stress Test and this psychology app will help you do something about the way you feel!

How stressed are you? Take a Stress Test & measure your stress level RIGHT NOW!


■STRESS TEST FEATURES■


◼Stress Test provides useful indication of your mental health
◼This psychological test is self-assessment tool
◼Online test always available to you
◼Helps you identify whether you have signs and symptoms of stress
◼Helps you figure out the next best step for you
◼Stress Test is confidential & anonymous


Psychological tests assess and evaluate information based on your answers, which is why the formal name of psychological testing is a psychological assessment. Psychological test’s accuracy depends on how carefully and seriously you answer the questions you’re asked. This self-assessment psychological test is not a diagnosis tool, but can help you discover your options and give you starting point. This psychology test can help you learn something about your personality and how certain symptoms can affect your everyday life. Take a test and improve your self-awareness for personal growth and development.  


■DISCLAIMER■


The screening tests and other psychological self-tests provided on “BalkanboyMedia” are intended to be used within the context of evaluation and education.

These tests are not intended to be a substitute for professional psychological, psychiatric or medical advice, assessment, diagnosis, or treatment.

The author, provider, and publisher of this test disclaims liability, loss, or risk incurred as a consequence, directly or indirectly, from the use and application of any of this material.

Results of the test will not be used for any other purpose than for your own personal use.


BalkanboyMedia attaches great importance to protecting our users’ privacy and data. BalkanboyMedia records absolutely no data and test results from our visitors. BalkanboyMedia does not collect any test results which we could distribute. BalkanboyMedia does not transmit any personal information and test results to third party. BalkanboyMedia protects your privacy by means of our policy not to collect any data.
